  --instance-ids i-YOURINSTANCEID \
  --media-snapshot-id snap-YOURSNAPSHOTID \
  --max-concurrency 1
Then watch what happens:
bashpython monitor.py \
  --profile YOUR_PROFILE \
  --batch-id batch-evergreen2026-pilot-001 \
  --watch
If the automation fails at any step, tell me the error and I'll fix the code. That's how we should be doing this — run it, see what breaks, fix it. Not pre-flight checklists that duplicate what the automation is supposed to do.
